CONTENTS OF THIS FILE
---------------------

 * Installation
 * Obtain your Pandora username
 * Download your music!


INSTALLATION
------------

- PandoraExtractor can run without installation. Yay!


OBTAIN YOUR PANDORA USERNAME
----------------------------

- Sign in to your Pandora account. Don't ask me how!
- When you are in, click your email address on the top-right corner of the page,
and select "My Profile"
- In the profile page, your username is right next to your profile picture. You 
can also see it in the URL appeared on your web browser address bar
    For example: http://www.pandora.com/profile/littlefinzer
    -> My Pandora username is: littlefinzer
- Remember it!


DOWNLOAD YOUR MUSIC!
--------------------

- Open "PandoraExtractor.exe". At the first time loading this file, your AntiVirus 
software may proceed to scan it. Let it do so for about a minute.
- All music tracks will be saved under "MY_MUSIC" folder, grouped by the Pandora
station name to which they belong
- Enjoy!
